ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
1 (3 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des:
"This light dip goes quickly at parties. Be prepared with the recipe! It goes well with apples, bananas, strawberries, grapes, but not so much with melon-type fruits. 
It also makes a great pie filling in an OreoÂ® crust!"
ins: Mix whipped topping, pudding mix, milk, and coffee-flavored liqueur together in a bowl. Refrigerate dip until set, 1 hour to overnight.
